<h1><i class="fa fa-eye"></i>Viewing Chats</h1>

<ol class="breadcrumb">
	<li><a href="#help"><i class="fa fa-question-circle"></i>Help</a></li>
	<li><a href="#help/sharing-messages"><i class="fa fa-comment"></i>Sharing Messages</a></li>
	<li><i class="fa fa-eye"></i>Viewing Chats</li>
</ol>

<div class="content">
	<p>Sometimes you need to share information with a specific person rather than broadcasting the information to your entire group of friends.  For this application, <%= application.name %> includes the ability to exchange direct messages with your friends.  Direct messages can include images, files, or folders as attachments, which allows you to share just about anything via private direct messaging. </p>

	<ol>
		<li>
			<h2><i class="fa fa-comment"></i>The Chat Browser App</h2>
			<p>Direct messages allow you to send messages directly to one or more friends and are grouped in "chats".  A chat is a conversation with one more more friends.  To view your chats, click on the "Chat with Connections" icon in the session toolbar at the top of the screen. </p>

			<div class="figure">
				<img src="images/help/sharing-messages/viewing-chats/chat-with-friends-icon.png" />
				<div class="caption">Chat with Connections Icon</div>
			</div>

			<p>This will launch the <a href="#apps/chat-browser">Chat Browser</a> app, which you can use exchange direct messages with your friends. </p>

			<div class="figure">
				<a href="images/help/sharing-messages/viewing-chats/chat-browser.png" target="_blank" class="lightbox" title="The Chat Browser App"><img class="dialog" src="images/help/sharing-messages/viewing-chats/chat-browser.png" /></a>
				<div class="caption">The Chat Browser App</div>
			</div>
		</li>

		<li>
			<h2><i class="fa fa-comment"></i>Chats Sidebar Panel</h2>
			<p>A list of your current chat sessions is shown in the sidebar.  When you click on a chat icon, the <a href="#apps/chat-viewer">Text <%= config.apps['communicator'].name %></a> will switch to that particular chat. </p>

			<div class="figure">
				<img src="images/help/sharing-messages/viewing-chats/chats-sidebar.png" />
				<div class="caption">Chats List Sidebar</div>
			</div>
		</li>

		<li>
			<h2><i class="fa fa-comment"></i>Chat Conversations</h2>
			<p>A chat conversation is displayed as a list of messages with your messages shown on the left and the other chat participants' messages on the right. </p>

			<div class="figure">
				<img src="images/help/sharing-messages/viewing-chats/chat-conversation.png" />
				<div class="caption">A Chat Conversation</div>
			</div>
		</li>
	</ol>

</div>